Section.name: About BRHCET
Section.description:
B. R. Harne College of Engineering and Technology (BRHCET) was established in 2011 by Jai Shri Siddhivinayak Foundation. It is committed to impart quality education & training leading to various professional degrees and aims to be a global Institution through continual improvement. The Campus is spread over 11.7 Acres of Land with beautiful building coming up. It is situated at Thane, Mumbai. It offers under graduate and post graduate Engineering courses, MCA and MBA.
